      "type": "uofa:IntermediateResult",
      "name": "Synthesis of prior pedicle screw mechanics studies supporting model form and acceptance bound selection",
      "description": "A comprehensive synthesis of published experimental and computational studies on pedicle screw bending mechanics, including cadaveric constructs, titanium alloy material characterization, and prior ASTM F1717 datasets from the literature (Goel et al. 1991; Chao et al. 1993; Brodke et al. 1997; Bono et al. 2007; Nagaraja et al. 2011). This synthesis informed the 10% acceptance bound selection and the bilinear hardening constitutive model choice. It represents a mature, well-corroborated body of evidence drawn from multiple independent research groups and regulatory submissions."
